'''泛雅典娜节'''，又称泛雅典娜赛会（英语：Panathenaea）<ref>{{cite book | author=光明日报社 | title=博览群书 | publisher=[[光明日报出版社|光明日报出版社]] | issue= | year=2007 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=291MAQAAIAAJ | language= | access-date= | page= | archive-date=2021-10-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211001134747/https://books.google.com/books?id=291MAQAAIAAJ | dead-url=no }}</ref>是[[古希腊|古希腊]][[雅典|雅典]]自公元前566年起<ref>A Brief History of the Olympic Games by David C. Young. Wiley-Blackwell. 2004, p. 23</ref> 至公元3世纪<ref>Susan Heuck Allen, [https://books.google.com/books?id=rV8vyYn-qMgC&pg=PA39&lpg=PA39 Finding the walls of Troy: Frank Calvert and Heinrich Schliemann at Hisarlík] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rV8vyYn-qMgC&pg=PA39&lpg=PA39 |date=20211004230357 }}. University of California Press. 1999, p. 39.</ref>每四年举办一次为纪念雅典守护神、智慧女神[[雅典娜|雅典娜]]的宗教节日、仪式和运动会及文化活动，是雅典最重要的节日。除了体育竞技外，泛雅典娜赛会还包括诗歌和音乐比赛，参与者通常在赛会期间表演朗诵《奥德赛》和《伊利亚特》。

